lines.text: Do you know why we didn't help you up? It was because we wanted you to have the strength to do it own your own
Human's are born alone and die alone
I finally realized I'm not alone... Wiseman
All who break the taboo and the rules of the space time corridor... shall be eliminated...!
Ami-chan! You don't want to hang around a bad influence like Usagi!
Please Sailor Moon, purify me...
Moon Princess Halation!
Cleansing...!
I've lost everything!
No, Cooan, your new life starts now!
Ha! I wouldn't care if one or two more worthless pieces of scum died.
How dare she!
No! Sailor Warriors, she's seriously our sister, it's that wand that's possessing her!
GO TO HELL!
Promise ring!
Pro Wresling?
[Imagines Naru and Umino wrestling]
How kinky...
O nothingness, O darkness Guide me to the resurrection of the Death Phantom, almighty god of the universe
So that Wiseman was up to something behind our back... Damn Him!
You've seen too much, so I must send you to your grave!
Wiseman! You damn bastard!
Love isn't something you take, it's something you gain
So I was wrong...
An error doesn't become a mistake unless you refuse to change it
[Wiseman watches behind the Pillar]
How could you let such an idiot persuade you so easily?
